org.qbroker.jndi

Class ImqWrapperCtx

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.qbroker.jndi.WrapperCtx
      • org.qbroker.jndi.ImqWrapperCtx
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    javax.naming.Context

    public class ImqWrapperCtx
extends WrapperCtx
    ImqWrapperCtx extends WrapperCtx and tries to init the context of CachedCtx with the real URL and the connection factory name. The connection factory name has to be defined in the query string as either "qcf=xxx" or "tcf=xxx" so that the object will be able to bind to the name.
